solution:
$\boldsymbol{E}_{0}=E_{0} \boldsymbol{e}_{x}$，而

$$
e_{\mathrm{r}} \times e_{x}=\cos \theta \cos \phi e_{\mathrm{r}}-\sin \phi e_{\theta}
$$

辐射光强即辐射平均能流密度，为

$$
\begin{aligned}
\overline{\boldsymbol{S}} & =\frac{1}{2} \operatorname{Re}\left\{\boldsymbol{E}^{*} \times \boldsymbol{H}\right\} \\
& =\frac{1}{2 \mu_{0}} \operatorname{Re}\left\{-c\left(\boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}} \times \boldsymbol{B}^{*}\right) \times \boldsymbol{B}\right\}
\end{aligned}
$$

由题图 5.4 知，$e_{\mathrm{r}} \cdot \boldsymbol{B}_{0}=0$，故得

$$
\overline{\boldsymbol{S}}=\frac{c}{2 \mu_{0}}|\boldsymbol{B}|^{2} \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}}=\frac{\mu_{0} q^{4} E_{0}^{2}}{32 \pi^{2} c m^{2} r^{2}}\left(\cos ^{2} \theta \cos ^{2} \phi+\sin ^{2} \phi\right) \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}}
$$

(c) 空间反射变换为

$$
\begin{array}{ll}
\boldsymbol{r} \rightarrow \boldsymbol{r}^{\prime} = -\boldsymbol{r}, & \nabla \rightarrow \nabla^{\prime} = -\nabla \\
\frac{\partial}{\partial t} \rightarrow \frac{\partial}{\partial t^{\prime}}, & e \rightarrow e^{\prime} = e
\end{array}
$$

显然此时有

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \rho(\boldsymbol{r}, t) \rightarrow \rho^{\prime}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) = \rho, \\
& \boldsymbol{j} \rightarrow \boldsymbol{j}^{\prime} = -\boldsymbol{j}
\end{aligned}
$$

由电荷守恒定律，再写出变换后不变形的麦克斯韦方程，仿（b）做法，可证明

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) = -\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{r}, t), \\
& \boldsymbol{B}^{\prime}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) = \boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)
\end{aligned}
$$

取圆环中心为原点，设空间点位置矢量为 \(\boldsymbol{r}(r, \theta, \varphi)\)，当 \( r \rightarrow \infty \) 时，该点的矢势为

\[
\boldsymbol{A}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) = \frac{i k \mu_{0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} k r}}{4 \pi r} \boldsymbol{n} \times \boldsymbol{m}
\]

式中，\(\boldsymbol{n} = \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}}, k = \frac{\omega}{c} \)，取复数形式的磁偶极矩

\[
\boldsymbol{m} = \pi a^{2} i_{0} \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega t} \boldsymbol{e}_{z}
\]

真实值理解为其实部，则得矢势公式为

\[
\boldsymbol{A}(r, t) = -i \frac{\mu_{0} \omega i_{0} a^{2} \sin \theta}{4 c r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\varphi}
\]

其相应的辐射电磁场为

\[
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{B} = \nabla \times \boldsymbol{A} = i k \boldsymbol{n} \times \boldsymbol{A} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{2} i_{0} a^{2} \sin \theta}{4 c^{2} r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\theta} \\
& \boldsymbol{E} = c \boldsymbol{B} \times \boldsymbol{n} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{2} i_{0} a^{2} \sin \theta}{4 c r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\varphi}
\end{aligned}
\]

平均能流密度为

\[
\begin{aligned}
\overline{\boldsymbol{S}} & = \frac{1}{2} \operatorname{Re}\left\{\boldsymbol{E}^{*} \times \boldsymbol{H}\right\} = \frac{c}{2 \mu_{0}} \operatorname{Re}\left\{\left(\boldsymbol{B}^{*} \times \boldsymbol{n}\right) \times \boldsymbol{B}\right\} \\
& = \frac{c}{2 \mu_{0}}|\boldsymbol{B}|^{2} \boldsymbol{n} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{4} i_{0}^{2} a^{4}}{32 c^{3} r^{2}} \sin^{2} \theta \boldsymbol{n}
\end{aligned}
\]

设 \( P \) 为平均辐射功率，辐射角分布为

\[
\frac{\mathrm{d} P}{\mathrm{~d} \Omega} = S r^{2} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{4} a^{4} i_{0}^{2}}{32 c^{3}} \sin^{2} \theta
\]
